gmx:name.gco:CharacterString: Feature catalog for Europe NUTS 3 Demographics, 2009-2014

gfc:definition.gco:CharacterString: The polygons represent areas of aggregated socioeconomic and demographic information at the NUTS 3 level for Europe.
The NUTS 3 code or the NUTS 0 code (with added "000") if there are no NUTS 3 geographical units for this country.
The name of the NUTS geographical unit or the country if there are no NUTS 3 geographical units for this country.
The NUTS 0 code for the country the NUTS graphical unit is in.
The population for the NUTS geographical unit in 2014.
The number of males for the NUTS geographical unit in 2014.
The number of females for the NUTS geographical unit in 2014.
The number of households for the NUTS geographical unit in 2014.
The average number of persons per household for the NUTS geographical unit in 2014.
The population growth rate for the NUTS geographical unit from 2009 to 2014 in percent.
The population per square kilometer for the NUTS geographical unit in 2014.
The number of dwellings for the NUTS geographical unit in 2014.
The number of people 0 to 14 years of age for the NUTS geographical unit in 2014.
The number of people 15 to 29 years of age for the NUTS geographical unit in 2014.
The number of people 30 to 44 years of age for the NUTS geographical unit in 2014.
The number of people 45 to 59 years of age for the NUTS geographical unit in 2014.
The number of people 60 years of age and over for the NUTS geographical unit in 2014.
The yearly amount of purchasing power (i.e., disposable income) for the NUTS geographical unit in Euro, in 2014, with ranges specific to each country.
The yearly amount of purchasing power (i.e., disposable income) for the NUTS geographical unit in Euro, in 2014, with ranges based on all European countries.
The purchasing power growth rate for the NUTS geographical unit from 2009 to 2014 in percent ranges.
The Gross Domestic Product in millions of Euro for the NUTS geographical unit in 2013.
The number of employed persons for the NUTS geographical unit in 2013.
The area of the NUTS geographical unit in square kilometers.
Area of feature in internal units squared.
